      <title>彭博监测：美联储决定 07/31/24</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/bloomberg-surveillance-the-fed-decides-07-31-24</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔恩·费罗、丽莎·阿布拉莫维奇和汤姆·基恩主持了《彭博观察》特别版，报道美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔的讲话。鲍威尔表示，美联储投票决定将基准利率维持在 20 多年来的最高水平后，最早可能在 9 月降息。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/bloomberg-surveillance-the-fed-decides-07-31-24</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 02:35:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>外资购买激增推动中国股市创下数月来最佳表现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/surge-in-foreign-buying-drove-china-stocks-best-day-in-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球基金周三抢购了价值 27 亿美元的中国股票，这一突然回归推动了中国股市出现五个多月来最佳涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/surge-in-foreign-buying-drove-china-stocks-best-day-in-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 02:32:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本超低抵押贷款利率 17 年来首次上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/japan-s-ultra-low-mortgages-to-see-first-increase-in-17-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行近二十年来第二次加息，将影响数百万个人抵押贷款，导致购房者的借贷成本在一代人以来首次上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/japan-s-ultra-low-mortgages-to-see-first-increase-in-17-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 02:09:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元强劲上涨，140 成为交易员的重要目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/-formidable-yen-rally-turns-140-into-a-big-target-for-traders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过 24 小时的激烈交易，日元创下了一年半多以来的最佳月度表现，Amundi 和道明证券的策略师预测日元兑美元汇率可能会升至 140。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/-formidable-yen-rally-turns-140-into-a-big-target-for-traders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 02:02:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛：日本银行利润将受到 20-30% 的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/goldman-japan-banks-to-see-profit-impact-of-20-30-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛日本金融分析师 Makoto Kuroda 讨论了日本央行加息对银行业的影响，以及大型银行的利润可能受到 20-30% 的影响。她在“彭博社：亚洲贸易”节目中与 Shery Ahn 和 Haidi Stroud-Watts 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/goldman-japan-banks-to-see-profit-impact-of-20-30-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 01:51:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元贬值致日本出口商股价创 2020 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/japan-s-stocks-tumble-most-since-march-as-exporters-falls-on-yen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股市暴跌，东证指数在全线抛售中创下2020年4月以来的最大跌幅，因为日元大幅上涨令出口商承压，央行加息拖累房地产股下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/japan-s-stocks-tumble-most-since-march-as-exporters-falls-on-yen</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 01:32:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据报道伊朗下令实施报复性打击，油价延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据报道，伊朗已下令对以色列实施报复性打击，以报复其在以色列领土上杀害一名哈马斯领导人，随后油价在周三飙升之后上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 23:26:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本股市抛售导致全球股市涨势停滞，日元上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股市创 2020 年以来最大跌幅，日元上涨，因交易员准备迎接日本央行进一步加息。受中东紧张局势影响，油价连续第二天上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 22:40:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>矿业强国澳大利亚将收紧勘探规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/mining-powerhouse-australia-to-tighten-up-rules-on-exploration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚——世界最重要的矿业国家之一——正计划加强管理公司如何公布勘探结果的规则，并将修改包括行业领导者必和必拓集团有限公司和力拓集团在内的上市公司的准则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/mining-powerhouse-australia-to-tighten-up-rules-on-exploration</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 14:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>央行将调整一年期贷款操作期限 政策转向</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/pboc-said-to-change-one-year-loan-operation-date-in-policy-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，中国央行计划将向国内银行注入一年期流动性的日期改为每月 25 日，作为向主要依靠短期利率引导市场的转变的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/pboc-said-to-change-one-year-loan-operation-date-in-policy-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 12:20:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
